            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0061_tls_001-1a.1" xml:lang="en">After king Zhuang had built the walls of Yulou, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0061_tls_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en">he asked Shenyin Zijing about it: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0061_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en">saying: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0061_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en">"I have finally built the walls of Yulou, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0061_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en">to provide the sacrifices of spring and autumn, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0061_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en">to store the remunerations of the neighboring states, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0061_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en">but how many [generations] of my descendants will protect it [how long will my reign last]? </seg>
                </p>

         </div>
